ss="classname">OCILob</a></span> to align with PHP naming standards.      </td>     </tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-ocilob.rewind-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member">{@link OCILob::seek}</li>    <li class="member">{@link OCILob::tell}</li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
